  <brief_title>Gene Expression in Patients With Advanced or Metastatic Colorectal Cancer Receiving Bevacizumab</brief_title>
  <official_title>Alternative Splice Forms of VEGF in Colorectal Cancer - Possible Value in Anti-VEGF Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
